Body: Description: Your appliance is running low on disk space, there is 161.89 gb free available from 950.16 gb (17%). EPP Server functionality and performance may be severely affected. Use Audit Log Backup to reduce the logs stored in the database, delete older system and audit log backups, and tune policies to reduce incoming log count. For further assistance contact Support.
What We've Learned Updated: Customer had space issues on their EPP server.
Next Steps Updated: Scheduled a remote session and clear over 150GB of older shadows.
